{
 "cells": [
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# 🛒 Проект 1: Воронка продаж E-commerce\\n",
    "\\n",
    "**Автор:** Евгений К. + Jack (Hermes Agent)\\n",
    "**Методология:** Human-in-the-Loop + Parallel Subagents + Persistent Memory\\n",
    "\\n",
    "## Цель\\n",
    "Понять, где в воронке теряются пользователи и какой канал/устройство приносит больше денег.\\n",
    "\\n",
    "## Данные\\n",
    "- 5,000 пользователей за 30 дней\\n",
    "- События: `view_product` → `add_to_cart` → `purchase`\\n",
    "- Атрибуты: канал привлечения, устройство, выручка"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import pandas as pd\\n",
    "import numpy as np\\n",
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\\n",
    "import seaborn as sns\\n",
    "\\n",
    "# Настройки визуализации\\n",
    "sns.set_style('whitegrid')\\n",
    "plt.rcParams['figure.figsize'] = (10, 6)\\n",
    "\\n",
    "# Загрузка данных\\n",
    "df = pd.read_csv('funnel_events.csv')\\n",
    "df['event_date'] = pd.to_datetime(df['event_date'])\\n",
    "\\n",
    "print(f\"Всего событий: {len(df):,}\")\\n",
    "print(f\"Период: {df['event_date'].min().date()} — {df['event_date'].max().date()}\")\\n",
    "df.head()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 1. Воронка по шагам"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Группировка по пользователям\\n",
    "users = df.groupby('user_id').agg(\\n",
    "    channel=('channel', 'first'),\\n",
    "    device=('device', 'first'),\\n    "    viewed=('event_type', lambda x: (x == 'view_product').sum()),\\n",
    "    carted=('event_type', lambda x: (x == 'add_to_cart').sum()),\\n",
    "    purchased=('event_type', lambda x: (x == 'purchase').sum()),\\n",
    "    revenue=('revenue', 'sum')\\n",
    ").reset_index()\\n",
    "\\n",
    "funnel_steps = {\\n",
    "    'Все пользователи': len(users),\\n",
    "    'Просмотрели товар': users['viewed'].sum(),\\n",
    "    'Добавили в корзину': users['carted'].sum(),\\n",
    "    'Совершили покупку': users['purchased'].sum()\\n",
    "}\\n",
    "\\n",
    "# Визуализация воронки\\n",
    "fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(10, 6))\\n",
    "steps = list(funnel_steps.keys())\\n",
    "values = list(funnel_steps.values())\\n",
    "colors = ['#3498db', '#2ecc71', '#f39c12', '#e74c3c']\\n",
    "\\n",
    "bars = ax.barh(steps, values, color=colors, edgecolor='black', linewidth=1.2)\\n",
    "\\n",
    "# Добавим проценты\\n",
    "for i, (bar, val) in enumerate(zip(bars, values)):\\n",
    "    pct = val / values[0] * 100 if i == 0 else val / values[i-1] * 100\\n",
    "    label = f\"{val:,} ({pct:.1f}%)\" if i > 0 else f\"{val:,}\"\\n",
    "    ax.text(bar.get_width() + 20, bar.get_y() + bar.get_height()/2, \\n",
    "            label, va='center', fontsize=12, fontweight='bold')\\n",
    "\\n",
    "ax.set_xlim(0, max(values) * 1.3)\\n",
    "ax.set_title('🎯 Воронка продаж', fontsize=16, fontweight='bold', pad=20)\\n",
    "ax.invert_yaxis()\\n",
    "plt.tight_layout()\\n",
    "plt.savefig('funnel_chart.png', dpi=150, bbox_inches='tight')\\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 2. Конверсия по каналам"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "channel_stats = users.groupby('channel').agg(\\n",
    "    total=('user_id', 'count'),\\n",
    "    buyers=('purchased', 'sum'),\\n",
    "    revenue=('revenue', 'sum')\\n",
    ").reset_index()\\n",
    "channel_stats['conversion_rate'] = channel_stats['buyers'] / channel_stats['total'] * 100\\n",
    "channel_stats['arpu'] = channel_stats['revenue'] / channel_stats['total']\\n",
    "channel_stats = channel_stats.sort_values('conversion_rate', ascending=True)\\n",
    "\\n",
    "fig, (ax1, ax2) = plt.subplots(1, 2, figsize=(14, 6))\\n",
    "\\n",
    "# Конверсия\\n",
    "bars1 = ax1.barh(channel_stats['channel'], channel_stats['conversion_rate'], color='#2ecc71', edgecolor='black')\\n",
    "ax1.set_xlabel('Конверсия (%)', fontsize=12)\\n",
    "ax1.set_title('Конверсия по каналам', fontsize=14, fontweight='bold')\\n",
    "for bar in bars1:\\n",
    "    ax1.text(bar.get_width() + 0.2, bar.get_y() + bar.get_height()/2, \\n",
    "             f\"{bar.get_width():.1f}%\", va='center', fontsize=11)\\n",
    "\\n",
    "# Выручка\\n",
    "bars2 = ax2.barh(channel_stats['channel'], channel_stats['revenue'], color='#3498db', edgecolor='black')\\n",
    "ax2.set_xlabel('Выручка ($)', fontsize=12)\\n",
    "ax2.set_title('Выручка по каналам', fontsize=14, fontweight='bold')\\n",
    "for bar in bars2:\\n",
    "    ax2.text(bar.get_width() + 200, bar.get_y() + bar.get_height()/2, \\n",
    "             f\"${bar.get_width():,.0f}\", va='center', fontsize=11)\\n",
    "\\n",
    "plt.tight_layout()\\n",
    "plt.savefig('channel_comparison.png', dpi=150, bbox_inches='tight')\\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 3. Конверсия по устройствам"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "device_stats = users.groupby('device').agg(\\n",
    "    total=('user_id', 'count'),\\n",
    "    buyers=('purchased', 'sum'),\\n",
    "    revenue=('revenue', 'sum')\\n",
    ").reset_index()\\n",
    "device_stats['conversion_rate'] = device_stats['buyers'] / device_stats['total'] * 100\\n",
    "device_stats = device_stats.sort_values('conversion_rate', ascending=False)\\n",
    "\\n",
    "fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(8, 5))\\n",
    "colors_device = ['#e74c3c', '#f39c12', '#3498db']\\n",
    "bars = ax.bar(device_stats['device'], device_stats['conversion_rate'], color=colors_device, edgecolor='black')\\n",
    "\\n",
    "for bar in bars:\\n",
    "    ax.text(bar.get_x() + bar.get_width()/2, bar.get_height() + 0.2, \\n",
    "            f\"{bar.get_height():.1f}%\", ha='center', fontsize=12, fontweight='bold')\\n",
    "\\n",
    "ax.set_ylabel('Конверсия (%)', fontsize=12)\\n",
    "ax.set_title('📱 Конверсия по устройствам', fontsize=14, fontweight='bold')\\n",
    "ax.set_ylim(0, max(device_stats['conversion_rate']) * 1.2)\\n",
    "plt.tight_layout()\\n",
    "plt.savefig('device_conversion.png', dpi=150, bbox_inches='tight')\\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 💡 Инсайты\\n",
    "\\n",
    "1. **Mobile проблема**: 9.2% конверсия против 11.0% на desktop — проверить UX оформления заказа на мобильном\\n",
    "2. **Referral лучший канал**: 11.5% конверсия, но маленький объём — масштабировать программу рефералов\\n",
    "3. **Paid social много трафика, низкая конверсия**: 9.2% — проверить качество аудитории и креативы"
   ]
  }
 ],
